text: The original Black Christmas is one of my favorite horror films of all time, this remake looks generically bland and dull in comparison. It doesn't even seem much like a remake at all, rather it just shares the same name. Part of the reason the original worked so well was because it was a product of the times, it's hard to recreate the same amount of tension, atmosphere and terror set in the modern day because of things like Caller ID's, Cell Phones, the internet etc. It also looks like one of those "Women fight back" horror films which is something that I feared ever since this was announced. I'm not even gonna waste my time with this, just re-watch the original instead.
